This print of mine is on sale now to benefit earthquake relief in Turkey and Syria. It’s a 10x12” inch print for $150. A lot of better, more prestigious photographers offering prints too check out @six.two.editions. 

Thank you to the force of nature @devinyalkin and the rest of the six two team for arranging everything. 

NOW LIVE for just 10 days. Purchase a print of this photograph and over 200 more at @six.two.editions to support earthquake relief efforts in Turkey & Syria.

SIX.TWO Editions is a photo print sale now running until March 20, in which over 200 photographers have generously and with open hearts made their work available for purchase at an affordable price to benefit recovery operations in Turkey & Syria after the devastating earthquakes of February 06. All net proceeds will be donated to vetted, non-governmental organizations leading the way in recovery efforts and organizational needs on the ground in the earthquake region.
